            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275176</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iMac 從 1998 年取代 Macintosh 至今 26 年，看到這個名字就會聯想到蘋果最具代表性的多合一電腦。不過從 2021 年開始，iMac 以純 24 吋熒幕、多彩機身示人，以活躍、輕巧纖薄的外觀，吸引 Apple 多合一電腦入門用家、輕電腦用家。今次 Apple 全新 iMac 配備 M4 處理器，並將基礎型號記憶體增至 16GB，令這部入門機都變得相當實用，在效能上滿足更多人需要。如果你是 iPhone、iPad 用家、學生用家，想家中有一部簡單、可為你做到更多事情的電腦，又或者想購入一部色彩奪目的電腦佈置你的家居或店鋪，就要繼續留意以下的評測，看看你在選擇 iMac 時應該要注意的地方。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03812.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03812-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03812-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03812.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03819.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03819-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03819-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03819.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>須知 <b>1</b>：設計與外觀</h2><p>2024 年的 24 吋 iMac 延續了 Apple 一貫的極簡設計，但這次的顏色系列增添了活力，色調變得更加鮮明且多樣化。包括藍色、紫色、粉紅、橘色、黃色、綠色和銀色，每個顏色都帶有些微的更新，令 iMac 不只是單純一部電腦，也是能為空間增色的時尚單品。今次我們借到的是綠色版本，更加鮮艷明亮，而另一個粉紅色版本亦都相當吸引。顏色不只體現在機身背部，連配件如鍵盤、滑鼠和充電線也同步配色。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111451800.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111451800-694x314.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="314" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111451800-694x314.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024111451800.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03852.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03852-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03852-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03852.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03822-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1275234" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03822-365x580.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="873" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03822-365x580.jpg 365w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03822-scaled.jpg 567w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 550px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03816.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275212" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03816-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03816-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03816.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03856.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03856-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03856-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03856.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03835.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275218" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03835-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03835-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03835.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲但要留意 iMac 需要這樣的電源變壓器提供電源，它的大小足有一隻滑鼠那麼大</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03839.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275220" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03839-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03839-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03839.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲3.5mm 耳筒插口佈置在機身左下角，設計也十分優雅</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03843.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275221" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03843-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03843-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03843.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>須知 <b>2</b>：可選配最新防反光玻璃</h2><p>M4 iMac 配備 24 吋 4.5K Retina 顯示器，畫質清晰細膩，適閤家庭娛樂、輕度設計以及學習用途。在市面上你很難找到 24 吋的 4.5K 這樣高解像度的顯示器，大部份在腦場看到的，都是 2K 甚至只有 1080p 解像度，畫質不能同日而語。在這部電腦上你都有 MacBook 上看到的畫質，不會看到「一粒粒」的液晶體像素點，畫面文字、視窗都十分平滑，配合 macOS 本身的設計，滿足到大家對美的追求。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03848.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275208" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03848-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03848-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03848.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03850.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03850-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03850-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03850.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>今次 iMac M4 版還提供了具防眩光效果的 Nano Texture「納米紋理顯示器」，能夠大幅減低反光現象，我們同未有裝設此玻璃的 iMac 比較，會看到天花板上的光、背面的環境，甚至用家自己本人都映照在一般玻璃當中，而納米紋理玻璃表面可大幅減低這種反光現象。但要留意納米紋理顯示器會稍為令畫面變暗一點（這點可靠增加畫面亮度來彌補），而色彩輸出的對比度會減弱一點。除非你是對顏色表現十分敏感的專業用户，否則對一般用家來説，防眩光玻璃就利大於害。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03806.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03806-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03806-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03806.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲在極端燈光場景，「納米紋理顯示器」可以大幅減低反光效果</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03808.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03808-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03808-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03808.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲以往 iMac 的畫面你經常會看到自己&#8230;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03807.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03807-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03807-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03807.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲「納米紋理顯示器」可大幅減輕這類反射</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03837.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03837-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03837-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03837.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「納米紋理顯示器」在開畫面後，反光情況就更低</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
